337
00:26:14,320 --> 00:26:17,596
Here you go, Bri.
I got chips and some jerky here.

338
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:19,870
If you want 'em, just holler.

339
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,392
Just in case.

340
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:32,835
<i>From the moment I began</i>
<i>working on the book...</i>

341
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:36,191
<i>... I found myself asking</i>
<i>one question over and over.</i>

342
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:40,359
<i>What's the difference</i>
