376
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:36,835
<i>At the time, I was angry that</i>
<i>Mr Baxter slammed the door in my face.</i>

377
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:39,110
<i>But it was just his way of forgetting...</i>

378
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:43,279
<i>... of pretending that nothing terrible</i>
<i>had ever happened there.</i>

379
00:29:43,400 --> 00:29:47,473
